In general Vanilla mutes flavours, EM also and the Straw Ripe has Ethyl Maltol  too. Is there really enough Strawberrytaste after a steep? &#xD;
Will the vanilla and the EM not mute the Strawberry? I will give it a try and report and rate after steeping.&#xD;
Update:  I like to add 1.5% OOO Strawberry Jam for the FA Juicy Strawberry, to make the other Strawberries a little Jam'ier.&#xD;
But its a solid, good recipe, how it is.
